ID_SPARTA_PREMIUM_PAGE_ARMIES_TEXT: Play as the French army in They Shall Not Pass and the Russian Empire in, In The Name of the Tsar.
ID_SPARTA_PREMIUM_PAGE_BATTLEPACKS_TEXT: Superior Battlepacks are more likely to drop rarer weapon skins. Each Battlepack is delivered monthly, starting November 2016.
ID_SPARTA_PREMIUM_PAGE_EARLY_ACCESS_TEXT: Be the first to get access to all new multiplayer maps.
ID_SPARTA_PREMIUM_PAGE_EARLY_ACCESS_TITL: TWO WEEK EARLY ACCESS TO EACH EXPANSION PACK
ID_SPARTA_PREMIUM_PAGE_GAMEMODES_TEXT: Unique new flavors of Battlefield 1 multiplayer awaits – with game modes such as Frontlines and Supply Drop.
ID_SPARTA_PREMIUM_PAGE_INTRO_TEXT: Get two weeks early access to new Battlefield 1 maps with Battlefield 1 Premium Pass. *
ID_SPARTA_PREMIUM_PAGE_INTRO_TITLE: EXPAND YOUR BATTLEFIELD 1 WITH BATTLEFIELD 1 PREMIUM PASS
ID_SPARTA_PREMIUM_PAGE_OUTRO_DISCLAMIER: * Stay tuned to www.battlefield.com/games/battlefield-1/premium for details and release dates for each expansion pack.
ID_SPARTA_PREMIUM_PAGE_OUTRO_TEXT: Expand the theater of all-out war with the Battlefield 1 Premium Pass. Get two weeks early access to new multiplayer maps, armies, and more in four themed digital expansion packs.
ID_SPARTA_PREMIUM_PAGE_VEHICLES_TEXT: Dominate the battlefield with new vehicles like the heavily armored St. Chamond tank and many more.
ID_SPARTA_PREMIUM_PAGE_WEAPONS_TEXT: Add all-new weapons to your arsenal with each new expansion included in Battlefield 1 Premium Pass.
ID_SPARTA_PREMIUM_PAGE_XPACK_TEXT2: Enter the war’s biggest front with the Russian army and fight in snow-covered ravines and a freezing archipelago in all new maps
ID_SPARTA_PREMIUM_PAGE_XPACK_TITLE: IN THE NAME OF THE TSAR
